    "Workers in our sample have been reweighted so all workplaces have the same weight.",
    "Panel (a) shows employers' policies on AI chatbot usage for work.",
    "Panel (b) indicates whether the employer has its own AI chatbot.",
    "Panel (c) reports whether workers have participated in AI chatbot training courses.",
    "Sample: All completed responses from the 2024 survey."
